bayou.jtype

Class TypeVar<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • bayou.jtype.JavaType<T>
      • bayou.jtype.ReferenceType<T>
        • bayou.jtype.TypeVar<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TypeArg

    public abstract class TypeVar<T>
extends ReferenceType<T>
    Type variable.

    A type variable may be

    • declared by a generic class/interface or a generic method/constructor
    • created by capture conversion
